Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.14,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:415937,417146}Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.60,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:417145,419607}I'm sure my brother will love these.{NOTE:兄もきっと喜ぶわ。}
