Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.77,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:715236,716779}Welcome back!{NOTE:おうおかえり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.40,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:716779,719406}How is Michael feeling?{NOTE:ミハエルさんの具合はどう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.95,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:719406,721951}Actually, he woke up a little while ago.{NOTE:実はさっき目を覚ましたんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.74,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:721951,725746}That's great. Avinia must be thrilled!{NOTE:よかったわね。アユリア喜んでいたんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:725746,727122}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.91,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:727122,728916}I see, I see. I'm happy for them!{NOTE:そっかそっか。よかったな～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.33,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:728916,731334}Alright, time to give my regards to my future older brother—{NOTE:よーし将来の俺の兄貴に挨拶を…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.75,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:731334,732753}Ow, ow, ow, ow!{NOTE:あててててっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.33,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:732753,734337}You're not going anywhere.{NOTE:あんたは行かなくてよし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.42,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:734337,735422}But why?{NOTE:何でだよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.92,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:735422,738926}When I get married to Avinia, Michael will be my older brother!{NOTE:俺がアユリアと結婚したらミハエルは兄さんなんだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:751814,753524}What a beautiful forest.{NOTE:豊かな森だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.65,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:753524,754650}It really is…{NOTE:本当に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:42.57,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:755442,762574}The scenery is totally different, and yet it resembles our Kuang Village. I wonder why?{NOTE:なぜだろうな。景色は全然違うのに似てる気がする。俺たちの故郷クアン村に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.91,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:762574,766912}Maybe that's the reason why Hakum Village felt so nostalgic.{NOTE:だからハクム村にいると懐かしい感じがするのかもしれません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:770833,774837}I wonder what's going on in our village these days?{NOTE:今どうなっているんだろうな俺たちの村は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.54,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:774837,777548}I don't think anyone lives there anymore.{NOTE:おそらく誰も住んでいないでしょうね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:02.55,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:778048,782553}Now that you mention it, we met a Barioth\Nwith an old wound in Kuang Village.{NOTE:そういえばクアン村で古い傷のあるベリオロスに会った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.34,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:782553,785347}It seemed like it was protecting the village.{NOTE:まるで村を守っているようだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.47,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:785347,786473}Like a guardian?{NOTE:守り神…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.47,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:786473,788475}It must be Frostfang's parent.{NOTE:それはヒョウガの親だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.93,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:788475,789935}His parent?{NOTE:親子なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.39,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:789935,791395}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:791395,794231}Maybe he's waiting for us?{NOTE:待ってくれているのかもしれないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:794231,796358}For us to come home.{NOTE:俺たちの帰りを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:796358,797943}I'm sure it's waiting.{NOTE:きっと待ってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:797943,800612}A kinship once bound can never be broken.{NOTE:一度結んだ絆は切れない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.44,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:800612,803449}A Monstie and its Rider will always be connected through kinship.{NOTE:オトモンとライダーは絆でつながってるからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:27.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:804283,807369}I want to rebuild Kuang Village.{NOTE:元に戻したい…クアン村を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:807369,810039}Then let's go!\NWe'll help you out!{NOTE:だったら戻そう！俺たちも手伝うし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.08,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:810039,813083}Yeah. We've rebuilt Hakum Village once before.{NOTE:うん。ハクム村だってみんなで復興させたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:39.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:814376,819923}To tell you the truth, I didn't feel any pleasure or accomplishment from defeating Anvis.{NOTE:実はアンヴィスを倒した後喜びも達成感も感じなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:820716,823594}I finally accomplished my long-time goal.{NOTE:自分の長年の願いがかなった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:823594,827973}But I only caused trouble\Nto so many people in the process…{NOTE:しかし結果的に大勢の人に迷惑を掛けてしまった…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:827973,829183}Still, I…{NOTE:なのに俺は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.89,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:829808,831894}I know how you feel.{NOTE:その気持ち俺は分かるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:831894,832936}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:59.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:833604,839360}I'm walking the right path again thanks to Lute.\NI want to help you the same way Lute helped me.{NOTE:リュートがいたから戻ってこられた俺は今は困った人がいるなら助けたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.61,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:839360,840611}Cheval…{NOTE:シュヴァル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.15,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:840611,842154}Isn't that how it should be?{NOTE:いいんじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:05.53,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:842154,845532}Everyone should think and act on their own!{NOTE:それぞれが自分で考え行動すればいいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:10.70,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:845532,850704}Even when we're apart,\Nwe're bound together through kinship.{NOTE:みんな別々な場所に散らばっても俺たちは絆で結ばれている！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.54,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:850704,853540}We'll be always together!{NOTE:いつだって集まれる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:853540,856043}That's our kinship!{NOTE:これが俺たちの絆だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:22.42,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:857711,862424}I see. So you've decided to return to your hometown?{NOTE:そうか。２人は自分の村に戻ることにしたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:862424,865594}Yes. Thank you very much for taking care of me.{NOTE:本当にお世話になりありがとうございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.22,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:865594,867221}Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:31.60,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:867221,871600}No, no. Riders help each other in need.{NOTE:よいよい。ライダー同士助けたり助けられたりじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:36.81,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:871600,876814}Chief Omna. I decided to go with them\Nto help rebuild Kuang Village.{NOTE:オムナ村長。俺もクアン村の復興を手伝うために一緒に行くことにしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.98,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:877481,880984}It seems you also met new friends by coming to our village, Debli.{NOTE:デブリもこの村に来てよい出会いをしたようじゃな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.27,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:880984,883278}Trust your judgment.{NOTE:自分の判断を信じなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.23,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:883277,884238}Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:884238,885948}Well then, Chief.{NOTE:でオムナ村長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.86,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:885948,889868}Lute, Cheval… each of you are going to embark on a journey, yes?{NOTE:リュートシュヴァルはそれぞれが旅に出るのじゃな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.91,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:889868,890911}Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:56.50,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:890911,896500}When youngsters are determined\Nto go on a journey, no one can stop them.{NOTE:若者は旅に出ると決まっているものじゃ。誰もそれは止められまい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.50,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:896500,899503}Chief Omna. We'll remain in the village for now.{NOTE:オムナ村長。僕たちは村に残ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.42,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:899503,902423}There's something we want to do here.{NOTE:私たちは村でやりたいことがあるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.38,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:902423,904382}I'll go with Lute—{NOTE:自分はリュート先輩と一緒に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.88,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:904382,905884}It's too early for you!{NOTE:あんたはまだ早い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.71,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:905884,906718}Tsk.{NOTE:ちぇっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.22,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:906718,909221}That's one difficult junior.{NOTE:手のかかる後輩がいるしね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.56,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:920691,921567}Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.06,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:921567,924069}What is it, Navirou?{NOTE:どうしたんだ？ナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:28.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:924069,928824}I heard you've decided to go on a journey again.{NOTE:聞いたぞリュート。どうやらまた旅に出ることにしたようだな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:928824,930033}That's right.{NOTE:そうなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.58,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:930033,934580}I saw people handling their Monsties differently than me.{NOTE:今度のことで俺とは違う形でオトモンと関わる人たちを見た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.33,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:934580,936331}And I thought to myself:{NOTE:そして思ったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:936331,938834}"I'd like to see more people."{NOTE:もっといろんな人を見てみたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:938834,940711}"What other forms kinship can take."{NOTE:いろんな形の絆をな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:45.17,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:940711,945174}Here we go with your "I want to see more stuff".{NOTE:まーたリュートの｢いろんなものを見てみたい｣が始まったか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:945174,947134}Navirou wants to take it easy for now.{NOTE:ナビルーは当分のんびりしたいぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.63,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:947134,949636}Then chill here at Hakum Village.{NOTE:ハクム村でのんびりしてろよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:53.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:949636,953182}Besides, shouldn't you go visit Pansy?{NOTE:それにお前ハナコのとこへも行かなきゃいけないんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:953182,955392}You promised her.{NOTE:約束してたよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.97,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:955392,956977}Yeah. Exactly.{NOTE:ああそのとおりだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:01.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:956977,961773}That's why, sorry, but this time\NI can't be your navigator.{NOTE:というわけで悪いが今回お前のナビはしてやれん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.19,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:961773,963192}Well, that's fine.{NOTE:あーいいいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:963192,965736}Your navigation is right only 1% of the time.{NOTE:お前のナビ100回に１回しか当たらないし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:965736,968322}What? It's 2% and you know it!{NOTE:何を言う！100回に２回は当たるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:968322,970782}Whatever. Besides, I'll have Ratha with me.{NOTE:いいって。俺にはレウスがついてるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.74,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:970782,972742}Oh, I see, I see. Well, bye then.{NOTE:ああそうかそうか。じゃあな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.03,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:973869,975037}You sure about that?{NOTE:本当にいいのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.49,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:975036,976497}It can't be helped.{NOTE:仕方ないだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.62,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:978040,980626}If you want me to come, now's the time to ask.{NOTE:ついてきてくださいと頼むなら今だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:980626,982628}I'll be fine, I'll be fine.{NOTE:大丈夫大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.17,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:982628,985172}Really? Are you really sure?{NOTE:本当か？本当にいいのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:985172,988508}Are you really, really, really, really, really sure about it?{NOTE:本当の本当の本当の本当の本当にいいのか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:989342,990886}Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.22,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:990886,992221}Navirou.{NOTE:ナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:992221,994681}Let's go together, Navirou!{NOTE:ずっとずっと一緒に行こうぜ、ナビルー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:994681,997642}Lute!{NOTE:リュート～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.81,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:998685,1001813}Oh, if you insist! I'll go with you!{NOTE:ふんっ仕方ない！ついていってやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.44,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001813,1004441}I'll go with Cheval, too.{NOTE:僕もシュヴァルさんにオトモします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.10,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004441,1006109}I'm counting on you.{NOTE:よろしく頼むよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.61,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006109,1008612}We discussed it between us and decided.{NOTE:ナンバーズで話し合って決めたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.40,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008612,1011406}Each of us will stay with our Riders.{NOTE:それぞれのライダーと一緒にいようってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.95,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011406,1013951}I'm looking forward to working with you, Beats!{NOTE:ビーツ先輩よろしくお願いします！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.70,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013951,1015702}Leave it to me!{NOTE:任しておけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.70,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015702,1017704}Mille-Mille, take care of me.{NOTE:ミルミルよろしくでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.91,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017704,1019915}You can count on me, Floof-Floof!{NOTE:大歓迎よチャモチャモ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.96,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019915,1023961}I think the two of us can show the Numbers' strength the most.{NOTE:僕たちナンバーズの力が一番発揮できると思うゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.37,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023961,1025378}I'm so glad you think that!{NOTE:うれしいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:09.34,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025378,1029341}I'll support you however I can, Avinia.{NOTE:私はこれからもアユリアをサポートさせてもらうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.63,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029341,1031635}Thank you.{NOTE:どうぞよろしくお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031635,1033595}So there's also kinship like this, too.{NOTE:こういう絆もあるんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.22,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035222,1036223}Michael…{NOTE:ミハエル…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:19.43,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036223,1039434}Can I stay with you?{NOTE:俺ミハエルと一緒にいてもいいかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.47,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039434,1040477}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040476,1043355}Let's build our kinship, too!{NOTE:俺たちはこれから絆をつくっていこう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.52,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043355,1044523}{NOTE:グシャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.31,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044523,1047317}I want a Felyne partner, too!{NOTE:俺もオトモアイルーが欲しくなったぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.61,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048068,1051613}And the boys set off on a journey again.{NOTE:そして少年たちは再び旅立つ。}
