Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.49,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057202,1058495}Lute! Cheval!{NOTE:リュート！シュヴァル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.62,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1059413,1060622}Lilia!?{NOTE:リリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:44.08,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061248,1064084}I received a letter from Loloa and rushed here.{NOTE:ロロアから手紙をもらって急いで来たのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.96,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064084,1065961}Why didn't you tell me?{NOTE:どうして教えてくれないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:50.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065961,1070591}I haven't decided where to go yet,\Nso I thought about letting you know later.{NOTE:どこへ行くのかまだ決めてないから落ち着いたら連絡しようと思ってたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.75,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070591,1072759}I bet you just forgot.{NOTE:ただ忘れていただけでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072759,1074595}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめん…ハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074595,1075971}Cheval, you too!{NOTE:シュヴァルもよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.72,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075971,1077723}I'm sorry…{NOTE:ごめんなさい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.55,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077723,1079558}Alright. I'll let it slide.{NOTE:うん許してあげる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.51,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079558,1081518}At least I got to see you again.{NOTE:こうやって集まれたんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:06.02,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081518,1086023}When you two decide your future goals\Nand work to accomplish them…{NOTE:リュートもシュヴァルも自分で次の目標を決めてそこへ歩きだすって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.23,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086023,1088233}…I will support you on your way!{NOTE:…私断然応援しちゃうわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088233,1089359}Lilia.{NOTE:リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089359,1090152}Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.16,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100579,1104166}Cheval. Avinia. Michael.\NTime to go.{NOTE:シュヴァルアユリアミハエル出発しよう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.16,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1104166,1106168}See you!{NOTE:いってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.96,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1106376,1107961}{\an8}Take care!{NOTE:いってらっしゃーい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.17,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1107961,1109171}{\an8}Good luck!{NOTE:頑張ってね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.42,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1109171,1110422}{\an8}Please be careful!{NOTE:気を付けてね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.59,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1110422,1112591}{\an8}Bye bye!{NOTE:バイバイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112924,1114926}Lute! Cheval!\NSee you again!{NOTE:リュートシュヴァルまた会おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.05,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114926,1116053}Take care!{NOTE:お元気で！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116053,1117554}I'll drop by Kuang Village!{NOTE:クアン村にも行くよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117554,1119431}Till next time!{NOTE:２人ともまたね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122350,1125729}Let's rebuild Kuang Village just like Hakum Village.{NOTE:クアン村を蘇らせよう。ハクム村のように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.93,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125729,1126938}Yeah!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.64,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126937,1128649}Hey!{NOTE:お～い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:52.81,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128649,1132819}Leave it to me, Michael!{NOTE:その辺俺に任せてくれ～！ミハエル兄さ～ん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.44,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132819,1135447}Hey! Wait for me!{NOTE:お～い！待ってくれ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.28,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136156,1137282}Bye for now, Lute.{NOTE:じゃあリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137282,1139451}Yeah! See you, Cheval!{NOTE:おうまたな！シュヴァル！}
